numericFormatter.!description:
Customize the global numeric formatter. If you set a formatter, it will replace the existing formatter. This function will take effect globally.

Example: <pre>
var customerFormatter = {
    format : function(value, pattern) {
        // add your codes here to convert number value to formatted string
        // according to the pattern string
        return formattedString;
    }
};
sap.viz.ui5.api.env.Format.numericFormatter(customerFormatter);
</pre>

